name: "Peony" wedding invitations from Sweet Graphics - ecru
description:
Make the first impression special with this luxurious vintage design of peonies.

The invitation card is printed on a gorgeous weighty pearl iridescent card stock.

The envelope has a beautiful gold shine to it, and is printed with the design to complement the set.

Sizes: invitation card - W143 x H200mm
envelope - C5 (W229 x H162mm)

The design is available in 2 colours:
Mint
Ecru

Other items available in this design:

RSVP card with envelope (W100 x H143mm)
Save the date postcard (W100 x H143mm)
Thank you card (W143 x H100mm)

Information card (W143 x H100mm)
Menu (W143 x H100mm)

Name card (W72 x H50mm when folded)

Seating plan: A4 (W210 x H297mm)
A1 (W594 x H841mm)

------------------------------------------------

Please see "How to place a full order" page for information on how to order.

name: "Dahlia" wedding invitation and RSVP card set - Green
description:
Make the first impression much more special with this luxurious wedding stationery.

The invitation card is printed on both sides on a gorgeous champagne iridescent paper, a weighty stock of 400gsm!
RSVP card is printed one side, on iridescent paper stock of 250gsm.

The envelope has a beautiful gold shine to it, and is printed with the design to complement the set.


The set consists of:

-Large invitation card (size W143 x H200mm) and envelope
-RSVP card (size W100 x H143mm) and envelope


The design is available in 2 colours:
Green
Pink
